We can move these constructions to setUniqueQualifiedName method and write this:
    protected void setUniqueQualifiedNameIfBlank(Node node) {
               if (StringUtils.isBlank(node.getQualifiedName())) {
                    node.setQualifiedName(node.getName() + "." + UUID.randomUUID().toString());
                }
    }

And then remove duplicate code.
StringUtils.isBlank specification:
 StringUtils.isBlank(null)      = true
 StringUtils.isBlank("")        = true  
 StringUtils.isBlank(" ")       = true  
 StringUtils.isBlank("bob")     = false

